Commit Message: Initial concept drafting for quantum cryptography demo

Journal Entry:

Brainstormed the idea for a quantum cryptography simulator for an upcoming hackathon.

Wrote basic notes on BB84 protocol and how to simplify it for beginners.

Planned out features like Alice-Bob base selection and simple animations.

Created a rough sketch of the homepage design on paper.

Started folder structure with index.html, main.css, and main.js.

